data.description: Escape the hustle and bustle of city life and step into this captivating 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence nestled on a vast 2.1-acre property. This home combines the charm of countryside living with modern conveniences, including a solar power system for more than enough sustainable energy. While it may require a little cleanup to restore its true luster, this property has all the potential to become your dream home.    Take advantage of the opportunity to purchase the neighboring property as well adding another 2.10 acres of fenced land to your estate.
